text: Lisa Hörnblad (born 6 March 1996) is a Swedish alpine skier, specialising in the speed events of Downhill and Super-G. She represented Sweden at the 2017 World Championships in St Moritz. and at the 2018 Olympics in Pyeongchang as well. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Swedish female alpine skiers Category:Alpine skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Sweden Category:Living people
